						               													<description>&amp;quot;The Jersey Shore Battle Games [previously known as the Sandy Hook Battle Games] are a group of simple, easy-to-play miniature battle games developed for one purpose: FUN! Unlike conventional board and miniature games, Jersey Shore Battle Games dispense with complexities altogether. Our goal is to provide a game that can be set up and played spontaneously, without studying complicated rules or spending extra money for expensive miniatures. Everything has to be commonly available.&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The components required for play are kite string, two six-sided dice, a sand pail, a cup, a disk segmented into quarters (i.e. lines marked on a paper plate), and the appropriate toy figures.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The basic system rules are available for free.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The following games use the Jersey Shore Battle Games rules system:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Castle Cracker&amp;#10;    Muskets and Sandpiles&amp;#10;    Operation Sandtrap&amp;#10;    Planetary Sand&amp;#10;    Sahara Sandstorm&amp;#10;    Sandarticus&amp;#10;    Sandpit Showdown&amp;#10;    Tanegashima Sandman&amp;#10;    Treasure of Sandheap&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
